				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/B%C3%A0-H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-irsg7oVzDXWkTsDwFBw8dA">Bà Hướng tự - 婆向寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-KrhE9fPPdxg7MJNECyal4Q">Phạm Viết Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/C%E1%BB%95-du%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-y1DEERPb1foNOuYfDE3Leg">Cổ duệ từ tự tự - 鼓枻詞自序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90%E1%BB%83-l%E1%BB%8B-Ho%C3%A0-Vinh-tri-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-1HNJFWKryAw1kNckvtkO5g">Để lị Hoà Vinh tri huyện - 抵莅和榮知縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Phan-K%E1%BB%89nh-Ch%E1%BB%89-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-phi%E1%BA%BFm-chu-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-giang-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-B9z7GIS_oJsKXk8fgwIPmA">Hoạ Phan Kỉnh Chỉ thu dạ phiếm chu Hương giang nguyên vận - 和潘敬止秋夜泛舟香江原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Minh-H%C3%A0nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/K%E1%BB%87/poem-QeT3LZfy552X3RiBQuc0_A">Kệ - 偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Minh-H%C3%A0nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-gx3bH_Y9n4kGEVhBqAwSTw">Minh Hành thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-h%C3%A0nh/poem-QCuVgwtzqWjFAv-gOpWJ3Q">Lương Châu hành - 涼州行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-g2WxJ4kB4whrtnw0PoPa7A">Đới Lương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-K%E1%BB%B3/Qu%C3%A1-Th%C3%A1nh-Qu%C3%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-UaeAJarCM1MsQDdHCNPCBg">Quá Thánh Quán tự - 大聖觀寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-K%E1%BB%B3/author-6RHyKOpqR_VZ_nmIcRKQxw">Trần Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-ca-gi%E1%BA%A3-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-lang/poem-zPyt2pQqiOXbnfgEtaIO6A">Tặng ca giả Trần lang - 贈歌者陳郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/author-cG-6f2ETrxSYJLcjUNmVzg">Trần Duy Tùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Choi-Chung/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA/poem-LAeoAIEMCyXJo8juzerxPw">Tuyệt cú - 絶句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Choi-Chung/author-_xWRnu55iB-En3b4xHFnmw">Choi Chung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BB%B1-Thi%C3%AAn-Ki%E1%BB%87n-h%E1%BB%93i-qu%C3%A1-L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-wTv176lWZ3zPw4CM8bHKzg">Tự Thiên Kiện hồi quá Lý Thường Kiệt miếu - 自天健回過李常傑廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-KrhE9fPPdxg7MJNECyal4Q">Phạm Viết Tuấn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
